  "subject": "Update dependencies",
  "commit_message": "Update dependencies\n\n- Upgrade Spring Boot from 4.0.3 to 4.0.4\n- Upgrade Swagger core from 2.2.43 to 2.2.45\n- Upgrade jackson-databind-nullable from 0.2.6 to 0.2.9\n- Upgrade springdoc-openapi from 2.8.6 to 2.8.14\n- Remove testcontainers-bom dependency (already in Spring Boot)\n- Remove CVE overrides in POM as Trivy reports zero CVEs\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5394\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I1105777ad50016f7eb865514db8b3a1672c46a9e\n",
